measurements.description: Twenty-four flowers well-arranged spirally around one 22-cm inflorescence; seven dark green leaves, midridge white up to 4.0cm wide, 7.5cm long; stem cordovan 14cm; sepals green overlaid rose; petals minute, green; tubular portion lip saccate, cordovan; distal portion lip bilobed, white; substance firm; texture matte; commended for shape and arrangement of flowers.
